Keep Nick Bot (KNB)
====================

This project now uses a Markdown README. Please open README.md for the full documentation, including:

- Project overview and feature list
- Installation and build instructions
- Configuration reference and command guide
- Links to the full technical documentation in docs/

Quick start (summary):

    cd src
    ./configure
    make dynamic
    cd ..
    cp cfg-examples/conf-ipv4 mybot.conf
    ./knb mybot.conf

Example configuration files are available in cfg-examples/.
Scripts for watchdog/cron integration are available in scripts/.

For detailed information, refer to README.md and the documentation set in docs/.
